\c 10
\s UJesu ubiza abaphostoli bakhe abalitshumi lambili
\p
\v 1 Wasebizela kuye abafundi bakhe abalitshumi lambili\x + Mark. 3.13-15; 6.7. Luka 6.13; 9.1.\x*, wabanika amandla phezu kwabomoya abangcolileyo, ukuthi babakhuphe, lokuthi belaphe sonke isifo lobuthakathaka bonke.
\p
\v 2 Njalo amabizo abaphostoli abalitshumi lambili yiwo la\x + Mark. 3.16-19. Luka 6.14-16. Seb. 1.13.\x*: Owokuqala nguSimoni othiwa nguPetro\x + 16.18. Joha. 1.42.\x*, loAndreya umfowabo\x + 4.18.\x*; uJakobe okaZebediya, loJohane umfowabo\x + 4.21.\x*;
\v 3 uFiliphu, loBartolomewu; uTomasi, loMathewu umthelisi\x + 9.9.\x*; uJakobe okaAlfewu, loLabewu othiwa njalo nguTadewu;
\v 4 uSimoni umKhanani\x + Luka 6.15. Seb. 1.13. Nani 25.11.\x*, loJudasi Iskariyothi laye owamnikelayo\x + 26.14,47; 27.3-5.\x*.
\s Ukuthunywa kwabaphostoli
\p
\v 5 Laba abalitshumi lambili uJesu wabathuma, wabalaya, esithi: Lingahambi ngendlela yabezizwe\x + 4.15.\x*, lingangeni emzini wamaSamariya\x + 2 Kho. 17.24. Ezra 4.10. Luka 9.52; 10.33; 17.16. Joha. 4.9,20; 8.48.\x*;
\v 6 kodwa yanini ikakhulu\x + 15.24. Seb. 13.46.\x* ezimvini ezilahlekileyo zendlu kaIsrayeli\x + 15.24. Hlab. 119.176. Jer. 50.6,17. Mat. 9.36.\x*.
\v 7 Futhi ekuhambeni kwenu tshumayelani, lisithi\x + Luka 9.2; 10.9. Mark. 6.12.\x*: Umbuso wamazulu usondele\x + 3.2.\x*.
\v 8 Silisani abagulayo, lihlambulule amalephero, livuse abafileyo, likhuphe amadimoni. Lemukeliswe ngesihle, phanini ngesihle\x + Roma 3.24. Isam. 21.6; 22.17. Seb. 8.20.\x*.
\v 9 Lingazithatheli igolide, loba isiliva\x + Mark. 6.8-11. Luka 9.3-5; 10.4-12. Luka 22.35.\x*, loba ithusi emixhakeni yenu\x + Mark. 6.8; 12.41.\x*,
\v 10 loba isikhwama sendlela, loba izigqoko ezimbili, loba amanyathela, loba udondolo\x + 1 Sam. 17.40. Luka 22.35,36.\x*; ngoba isisebenzi sifanele ukudla kwaso\x + 1 Kor. 9.7-14. 1 Tim. 5.18.\x*.
\v 11 Lakuwuphi umuzi kumbe umzana elingena kuwo, buzani ukuthi ngubani ofaneleyo kuwo; njalo lihlale khona, lize lisuke\x + 22.8.\x*.
\v 12 Njalo nxa lingena endlini, liyibingelele\x + 1 Sam. 25.6.\x*.
\v 13 Njalo uba indlu ifanele, ukuthula kwenu kakube phezu kwayo; kodwa uba ingafanele\x + 22.8.\x*, ukuthula kwenu kakubuyele kini\x + Hlab. 35.13.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo loba ngubani ongalemukeliyo kumbe ongalaleli amazwi enu, nxa liphuma kuleyondlu kumbe kulowomuzi, thintithani uthuli lwenyawo zenu\x + Seb. 13.51. Neh. 5.13. Seb. 18.6.\x*.
\v 15 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kuzakuba ngcono kulizwe leSodoma leleGomora ngosuku lwesigwebo, kulakulowomuzi\x + 11.22,24.\x*.
\s Abaphostoli bazahlutshwa
\p
\v 16 Khangelani, mina ngiyalithuma njengezimvu phakathi kwezimpisi\x + Luka 10.3.\x*; ngakho hlakaniphani njengezinyoka\x + Gen. 3.1. Mat. 25.2.\x*, libe msulwa njengamajuba.
\v 17 Kodwa limukani abantu; ngoba bazalinikela\x + 24.9.\x* emiphakathini\x + 5.22.\x*\x + Luka 12.11. Mark. 13.9,11-13. Luka 21.12-17.\x*, balitshaye ngesiswepu\x + 23.34. Seb. 22.19; 26.11. Seb. 5.40.\x* emasinagogeni abo\x + Luka 12.11. Mark. 13.9,11-13. Luka 21.12-17.\x*;
\v 18 njalo lizalethwa laphambi kwababusi lamakhosi ngenxa yami\x + Seb. 12.1; 24.10; 25.7,23. 2 Tim. 4.16.\x*, kube yibufakazi kubo lakwabezizwe\x + 8.4.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa nxa belinikela, lingakhathaleli ukuthi lizakhuluma njani kumbe into bani\x + 6.25.\x*; ngoba lizanikwa ngalelohola lokho elizakukhuluma\x + Eks. 4.12.\x*;
\v 20 ngoba kakusini elikhulumayo, kodwa \add ng\add*uMoya kaYihlo okhuluma phakathi kwenu\x + Luka 12.12. Seb. 4.8; 6.10. 2 Tim. 4.17.\x*.
\v 21 Futhi umfowabo uzanikela umfowabo ekufeni, loyise umntwana; labantwana bazavukela abazali, bababulale\x + Mika 7.6. Mat. 10.35,36. Mat. 24.10. Luka 12.53.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo lizazondwa yibo bonke ngenxa yebizo lami\x + 24.9.\x*; kodwa ophikelelayo kuze kube sekupheleni, nguye ozasindiswa\x + 4.13. Mark. 13.13. Dan. 12.12,13. Isam. 2.10.Heb. 3.6.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa nxa belizingela kulo umuzi\x + 23.34.\x*, balekelani komunye\x + 2.13; 12.15; 14.13. Seb. 8.1; 9.25; 14.6.\x*; ngoba ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kaliyikuqeda imizi yonke yakoIsrayeli, kuze kufike iNdodana yomuntu\x + 16.28.\x*.
\v 24 Umfundi kaphezu komfundisi, lenceku kayiphezu kwenkosi yayo.
\v 25 Kumanele umfundi ukuthi abe njengomfundisi wakhe, lenceku njengenkosi yayo\x + Luka 6.40. Joha. 13.16; 15.20.\x*. Aluba bebizile umninindlu \add ngokuthi\add* nguBhelezebhule\x + Mark. 3.22.\x*, kakhulu kangakanani labo abendlu yakhe?
\s UJesu uxwayisa abafundi bakhe
\p
\v 26 Ngakho lingabesabi; ngoba kakukho okufihliweyo, okungayikubonakaliswa; lokuthukuziweyo, okungayikwaziwa.
\v 27 Lokho engikutsho kini emnyameni, kukhulumeni ekukhanyeni; lalokho elikuzwa endlebeni, kumemezeleni phezu kwezindlu\x + Mark. 4.22. Luka 8.17. Luka 12.2-9.\x*.
\v 28 Njalo lingabesabi ababulala umzimba, kodwa bengelamandla okubulala umphefumulo\x + Isa. 8.12,13; 51.7,8,12,13. Jer. 1.8. 1 Pet. 3.14.\x*; kodwa mesabeni kakhulu olamandla okubhubhisa kokubili umphefumulo lomzimba\x + Jobe 37.24.\x* esihogweni\x + 5.22.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Kazithengiswa yini intaka ezimbili ngendibilitshi? Kodwa kakuyikuwa emhlabathini lanye yazo, ngaphandle kukaYihlo.
\v 30 Kodwa lezenu inwele zekhanda zibaliwe zonke\x + 1 Sam. 14.45.\x*.
\v 31 Ngakho lingesabi; lina liyazidlula intaka ezinengi\x + 12.12.\x*.
\p
\v 32 Ngakho ngulowo lalowo ozangivuma phambi kwabantu\x + Roma 10.9,10.\x*, lami ngizamvuma\x + Isam. 3.5.\x* phambi kukaBaba osemazulwini\x + 7.11.\x*.
\v 33 Kodwa loba ngubani ongiphika phambi kwabantu\x + Luka 12.9. 2 Tim. 2.12. 1 Joha. 2.23. Mark. 8.38. Luka 9.26.\x*, lami ngizamphika phambi kukaBaba osemazulwini\x + 7.11.\x*.
\s Izibonakaliso zezikhathi
\p
\v 34 Lingacabangi ukuthi ngize ukuletha ukuthula emhlabeni; angizanga ukuletha ukuthula, kodwa inkemba.
\v 35 Ngoba ngize ukwehlukanisa umuntu loyise, lendodakazi lonina, lomalokazana loninazala\x + 10.34,35, Luka 12.51-53.\x*;
\v 36 lezitha zomuntu ngabendlu yakhe.
\v 37 Othanda uyise kumbe unina kulami kangifanele; lothanda indodana kumbe indodakazi kulami kangifanele\x + Luka 14.26.\x*;
\v 38 longathathi isiphambano sakhe njalo angilandele, kangifanele\x + 16.24. Mark. 8.34. Luka 9.23; 14.27. Seb. 14.22.\x*.
\v 39 Lowo othola impilo yakhe uzalahlekelwa yiyo; lolahlekelwa yimpilo yakhe ngenxa yami uzayithola\x + 16.25 Mark. 8.35. Luka 9.24; 17.33. Joha. 12.25.\x*.
\v 40 Owemukela lina wemukela mina\x + Mark. 9.37. Luka 9.48. Joha. 12.44.\x*; lowemukela mina wemukela ongithumileyo\x + Mark. 9.37. Luka 9.48. Joha. 12.44.\x*.
\p
\v 41 Owemukela umprofethi ebizweni lomprofethi uzazuza umvuzo womprofethi\x + 1 Kho. 17.10; 18.4. 2 Kho. 4.8.\x*; lowemukela olungileyo ebizweni lolungileyo uzazuza umvuzo wolungileyo.
\v 42 Njalo loba ngubani ozanathisa omunye walababancinyane inkezo nje \add yamanzi\add* aqandayo ebizweni lomfundi, ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kasoze alahlekelwa ngumvuzo wakhe\x + 25.40. Mark. 9.41.Heb. 6.10.\x*.
